input_data = np.random.random_sample([1, 3, 32, 32, 32])
layer = lambda : Convolution3D(12, 5, 3, 4, dim_ordering='th', subsample=(1,
    2, 3), input_shape=(3, 32, 32, 32))
self.modelTestSingleLayerWithOrdersModes(input_data, layer, dim_orderings=[
    'th'], dump_weights=True, rtol=1e-05, atol=1e-05)
layer2 = lambda : Convolution3D(8, 6, 4, 2, dim_ordering='th', activation=
    'sigmoid', input_shape=(3, 32, 32, 32))
self.modelTestSingleLayerWithOrdersModes(input_data, layer2, dim_orderings=
    ['th'], dump_weights=True, rtol=1e-05, atol=1e-05)
layer3 = lambda : Convolution3D(16, 2, 2, 2, dim_ordering='th', bias=False,
    input_shape=(3, 32, 32, 32))
self.modelTestSingleLayerWithOrdersModes(input_data, layer3, dim_orderings=
    ['th'], dump_weights=True, rtol=1e-05, atol=1e-05)
